{"tid":1418573,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請將telegram推薦比身邊嘅長輩","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:56:47.000Z","uid":94075,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c12c18e3955a1ff1c5ca34d361ad387944f18273","tid":1418573,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:13:14.000Z","msg":"今日發完夢散完步，休息嘅時候見到有好多分化post。其實我全日都冇睇過連登，因為大部分資訊都係由tg spread開同埋可信性較高。我發覺一個問題就係每次有活動都會有好多分化post出現而且極有可能係三毛出嘅，係咪因為大部分出黎嘅人都唔太會上連登而專注於tg，所以三毛有機會控制到連登嘅風向? 我知道而家好多uncle auntie都有上連登，唔想你地比呢度嘅post牽着鼻子走。所以希望你地都download番telegram呢個app，然後叫你身邊嘅年輕人幫你入啲資訊站睇番啲啱嘅實時資訊。而手足都可以幫下你身邊嘅長輩download同入group。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"d31557a89964bcd4c3662b4d068c2ff52ebff502","tid":1418573,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:16:36.000Z","msg":"有咩channel易入口<br />\n想偷偷地幫深藍啊爸john<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f39e58e4889d342f2529b203ec66261a97c7065","tid":1418573,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:16:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1bb0d2c92395f0d0fcf81be5ade0471bc941b24","tid":1418573,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d31557a89964bcd4c3662b4d068c2ff52ebff502","tid":1418573,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:16:36.000Z","msg":"有咩channel易入口<br />\n想偷偷地幫深藍啊爸john<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:18:56.000Z","msg":"紅磚 中大？因為有channel好多實時資訊，驚佢地覺得太煩成日響咁"},{"pid":"881d069d419cecda670b996e2416a884af9a9001","tid":1418573,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:19:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4eeecb7c2041bd7fdc71e94e0488aaf99766415","tid":1418573,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:28:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"833cbd61d755dba28e479fab018e90cc97e26bbf","tid":1418573,"uid":24650